    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163360/extras/6f0c977ca5be74b3a7a32bcd6d87d885.poster.avif?t=1728240802\" width=608 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163360/extras/6f0c977ca5be74b3a7a32bcd6d87d885.webm?t=1728240802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163360/extras/6f0c977ca5be74b3a7a32bcd6d87d885.mp4?t=1728240802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163360/extras/f19187f8f54b6ac2817e4888028f36a0.webp?t=1728240802\" width=600 height=40 /></span>The doomsday cult 'The Eclipse Covenant' has unleashed a black hole on Earth, threatening to devour reality in their quest to transcend humanity. But their plan is unravelling. Harness gravity-defying powers to dismantle the cult and uncover the dark secrets they’ve buried. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163360/extras/7444872693358b4f0dffc01107111d68.poster.avif?t=1728240802\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163360/extras/7444872693358b4f0dffc01107111d68.webm?t=1728240802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163360/extras/7444872693358b4f0dffc01107111d68.mp4?t=1728240802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163360/extras/eeae5c6c0a1018bf85a66443392f3d24.webp?t=1728240802\" width=600 height=40 /></span>Is the black hole your ally—or your enemy? As it whispers cryptic words in your ear, you gain new powers. Is it guiding you to destroy the cult, or is this all part of a twisted game? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163360/extras/b12676e80997f2112e8882ddbf307241.poster.avif?t=1728240802\" width=608 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163360/extras/b12676e80997f2112e8882ddbf307241.webm?t=1728240802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163360/extras/b12676e80997f2112e8882ddbf307241.mp4?t=1728240802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163360/extras/8a464b35cc283fbc743e5b403d2bf2ea.webp?t=1728240802\" width=600 height=40 /></span>You're not the only one with new powers. Master the environment and keep moving to dodge relentless waves of beautiful yet deadly bullet hell patterns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163360/extras/9d6901af687dbcd9fc83fdec5e5bbd70.poster.avif?t=1728240802\" width=608 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163360/extras/9d6901af687dbcd9fc83fdec5e5bbd70.webm?t=1728240802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163360/extras/9d6901af687dbcd9fc83fdec5e5bbd70.mp4?t=1728240802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163360/extras/5b3f673d97d4b30e4f0b91024650f9aa.webp?t=1728240802\" width=600 height=40 /></span>With dynamic gravity in play, enemies adapt to wild angles and shifting perspectives, making you rethink every encounter. Outsmart the AI that uses gravity’s chaos to strike from any direction, turning each battle into a thrilling challenge!</p>",
